Odin Project > Foundations > JavaScript Basics > Calculaotr Progect

> Simple calculator:
    > Single 18 character display.
    > Displays number,opp,number or result.
    > Impliments add, subtract, mutiply and divide operations.
    > Display clear implimented
    > Error detection for not-a-number, infinity (divide by zero) and memory (result > 18 characters)
    > Uses font 'VT323' from https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=VT323&display=swap

> Extra credit
    > Handles floats to 2 decimal places
    > Backspace to delete last character
    > One decimal can be entered per number
    > Keyboard shortcuts; implimented by calling relevent button click events after the keyboard keypress event is detected
